* Zyber smiled at Rowdy Wolf, so, he HAD heard her stomach growl. She looked 
longingly at the herd of deer across the field and her stomach growled 
again, she sighed.*

" In a matter of fact, I am...a little."

* She disliked being in robot mode for to long, it made her feel too 
unnatural for her taste. Zyber stood still...*

" Beast Mode!"

* Now transformed she sat on her haunches and curled her tail around her, 
she sniffed the air as her stomach growled for the fourth time. The sent of 
the deer was so inviting and she was so hungry, she looked towards them and 
felt her mouth water.But she was in the company of another bot and it would 
be impolite to just run off and bring down her prey. She sighed and looked 
back at Rowdy Wolf, it was much more important to speak with a bot then to 
feed one's stomach.*
